Title: Landau Levels in the noncommutative $AdS_2$

Authors: R. Iengo (SISSA), R. Ramachandran (IMSc)

Comments: 19 pages, Latex, references and clarifications added including 2

figuresSystems and Quantum Hall EffectJournal-ref: JHEP 0202 (2002) 017

We formulate the Landau problem in the context of the noncommutative analogof a surface of constant negative curvature, that is $AdS_2$ surface, andobtain the spectrum and contrast the same with the Landau levels one finds inthe case of the commutative $AdS_2$ space.